{"tid":1372354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日食元朗b仔   請各位入嚟睇一睇食評","createTime":"2019-07-27T12:01:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T12:25:17.000Z","uid":129790,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e19fbaa661e6edc83ca1eebe8bd155e399f81fe5","tid":1372354,"uid":129790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:01:23.000Z","msg":"1. 人鏈係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好重\u0000要</span></span> 除咗遞物資去俾前面<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人鏈仲可以幫助傳遞信息</span></span>  <br />\n<br />\n今日前後來回跑咗幾次睇情況同傳達信息<br />\n但其實呢件事可以係人鏈做得到<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">除咗講需要乜嘢同唔需要乜嘢之外，請幫手向後傳一傳信息，等後面嘅人大概了解發生緊咩事   同埋唔會郁下就跑</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2. 士氣係好緊要， 口號可以適當嗌，但係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">敲護欄之類請避免。</span></span>  今日企後排嘅人聽到啲聲但唔知咩事其實好多人會好驚，跟住就好容易見到少少騷動就跑<br />\n<br />\n3.請真係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">做好心理準備出嚟</span></span> 出嚟之前請諗清楚自己今日想和理非，後援定勇武。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果想和理非，遊行完自行離開</span></span> 各人有自己嘅決定，留翻決定權俾人地。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果想後援，基本防護措施請你做好</span></span>  就算幫手傳遞物資自己戴翻個口罩係基本 同埋幫手傳一傳信息去後面 好多時後面嘅人根本唔知發生咩事 好容易驚慌失措<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔齊裝咪撚同我勇武</span></span> 要上前線請真係戴齊嘢 各人照顧好自己保護好自己<br />\n<br />\n最後 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">各位加油</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">利申我講緊B仔入邊幫手遞嘢食</span>"},{"pid":"c7451d9229606f31f22f64060a074e6fdb83380c","tid":1372354,"uid":129790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:02:20.000Z","msg":"毒撚自推"},{"pid":"04013b8e7c79c4f8314be40f25fc1844c71c5cda","tid":1372354,"uid":129790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:03:05.000Z","msg":"毒撚自推"},{"pid":"9e89dfb1ff3403b25229636d8aead7d38121e340","tid":1372354,"uid":129790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:04:29.000Z","msg":"Sor 應該開飲食台"},{"pid":"a835f7582cbd4243d64b52c1acd2dfaf91439d5f","tid":1372354,"uid":50776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:25:17.000Z","msg":"講得冇錯"}]}